TITLE: Installing Jazz using create-jazz-app CLI
DESCRIPTION: Command to create a new Jazz project using the create-jazz-app CLI tool with an API key parameter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/garden-co/jazz/blob/main/homepage/homepage/content/docs/index.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
npx create-jazz-app@latest --api-key you@example.com
```

