TITLE: Using useAccount Hook for User Projects in React
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the useAccount hook to access the current user's account, including deep loading of projects and tasks. It demonstrates handling loading states and rendering user projects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/garden-co/jazz/blob/main/homepage/homepage/content/docs/using-covalues/subscription-and-loading.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_3

