TITLE: Creating and Managing Projects in React - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet depicts the React component App, which handles creation, management, and rendering of projects and their associated issues using hooks and Jazz Tools.
SOURCE: https://github.com/garden-co/jazz/blob/main/homepage/homepage/content/docs/guide/react.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_12

